7 An Act relating to nuisance; amending 50 O.S. 2021,
Section 21, which relates to certain unlawful acts;
8 modifying provisions related to actions resulting in
certain felony convictions; making certain unlawful
9 acts a public nuisance; and providing an effective
date.
10
11
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 50 O.S. 2021, Section 21, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 21. The repeated use of any real property or structure
16 thereon to commit unlawful drug distribution, prostitution, or human
17 and/or sex trafficking acts which result in a felony conviction
18 under the Oklahoma Uniform Controlled Dangerous Substances Act may
19 shall constitute a public nuisance.
20 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
